{"title":"辛苦的老园丁","time_limit":1000,"memory_limit":125,"url":"http://www.joyoi.cn/problem/codevs-4672","statement":[{"title":"","format":"html_final","require":["katex"],"content":"\n<div class=\"panel panel-default\">\n<div class=\"area-title\">\n<span>\n题目描述\n<small>Description</small>\n</span></div>\n<div class=\"panel-body\">\n\n<p>老园丁有一个大花园，里面有N种花，每种花有一个魅力值。然而一只邪恶的鸡对花释放了邪恶魔法，使有些种类的花一旦同时出现在花园里就会一起枯死。老园丁很苦恼，希望你帮助他求出怎样选择留下的花，使得花不会枯死的情况下，魅力值之和最大。<br></p>\n\n</div>\n</div>\n\n<div class=\"panel panel-default\">\n<div class=\"area-title\">\n<span>\n输入描述\n<small>Input Description</small>\n</span></div>\n<div class=\"panel-body\">\n<p>第一行给出N,M。</p><p>接下来N行每行一个数表示魅力值。(第1种到第N种依次给出)</p><p>再接下来M行，每行两个数x,y，表示第x种花和第y种花不能同时存在。<br></p>\n\n</div>\n</div>\n<div  class=\"panel panel-default\">\n<div class=\"area-title\">\n<span>\n输出描述\n<small>Output Description</small>\n</span></div>\n<div class=\"panel-body\">\n\n<p>一个数，满足条件的所有花的魅力值之和的最大值。<br/></p>\n\n</div>\n</div>\n\n\n<div class=\"panel panel-default\">\n<div class=\"area-title\">\n<span>\n样例输入\n<small>Sample Input</small>\n</span></div>\n<div class=\"panel-body\">\n<p>4 3</p><p>1</p><p>2</p><p>3</p><p>4<br></p><p>1 2</p><p>1 3</p><p>2 3<br></p>\n\n</div>\n</div>\n\n<div class=\"panel panel-default\">\n<div class=\"area-title\">\n<span>\n样例输出\n<small>Sample Output</small>\n</span></div>\n<div class=\"panel-body\">\n<p>6<br></p>\n\n</div>\n</div>\n\n<div class=\"panel panel-default\">\n<div class=\"area-title\">\n<span>\n数据范围及提示\n<small>Data Size & Hint</small>\n</span></div>\n<div class=\"panel-body\">\n<p>1&lt;=N&lt;=25</p><p>1&lt;=M&lt;=40</p><p>输入数据保证x≠y，答案&lt;2^30<br></p>\n</div>\n</div>\n"}]}